{"id": "art-85", "label": "Art. 85", "title": "Art. 85", "slug": "art-85", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 85 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>(1)<span\nclass=SpellE>Asocia&#355;ii</span> sunt <span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;i</span>\nnelimitat <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> solidar pentru <span class=SpellE>opera&#355;iunile</span>\nîndeplinite în numele <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> de\npersoanele care o reprezint&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(2)Hot&#259;rârea\njudec&#259;toreasc&#259; <span class=SpellE>ob&#355;inut&#259;</span> împotriva\n<span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> este opozabil&#259;\nfiec&#259;rui asociat.</span></p>"}